com.codename1.rad.attributes

Class TableCellRendererAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.rad.models.Attribute<TableCellRenderer>
      • com.codename1.rad.attributes.TableCellRendererAttribute

  • public class TableCellRendererAttribute
extends Attribute<TableCellRenderer>

    An attribute for specifying the TableCellRenderer of a a Table. This can be added to any Node, as interested views can obtain it using Node.findInheritedAttribute(java.lang.Class).

    The primary target of this attribute is the FieldNode with the WidgetTypes.TABLE type (ie. com.codename1.rad.ui.UI#table(com.codename1.rad.models.Attribute…​) .

    See Also:
    com.codename1.rad.ui.UI#table(com.codename1.rad.models.Attribute…​), UI.cellRenderer(ca.weblite.shared.components.table.TableCellRenderer)
